name: INCallRecordTypeOptions
desc: Constants describing the types of calls to include during a search.

items.name: static var outgoing: INCallRecordTypeOptions
items.desc: A call initiated by the user.

items.name: static var missed: INCallRecordTypeOptions
items.desc: A call received by the user that went unanswered.

items.name: static var received: INCallRecordTypeOptions
items.desc: A received call that the user answered.

items.name: static var latest: INCallRecordTypeOptions
items.desc: The most recent call involving the user.

items.name: static var voicemail: INCallRecordTypeOptions
items.desc: A voicemail left from a missed call.

items.name: static var ringing: INCallRecordTypeOptions
items.desc: An incoming call that is currently causing the userâ€™s phone to ring.

items.name: static var inProgress: INCallRecordTypeOptions
items.desc: A received call that is currently in progress.

items.name: static var onHold: INCallRecordTypeOptions
items.desc: A received call that the user has put on hold.
